version_description: Thanks for using the JustPark app. This release brings you an improved help centre, a decluttered main menu, and redesigned screens for adding new payment methods and vehicles.

Thanks for using the JustPark app. This release brings you various redesigned screens, making it easier than ever to view information about a parking space, pay for it and then see details about your booking. We’ve also added an iPad version of our app, so you can now have your account and bookings on both your iPhone and an iPad, making for an even more seamless experience.

Thank you for using the JustPark app. In this release we've focused on making search even easier to use.

Now when you search we pull in all possible results within a 3 km radius - no more panning around and waiting for results to load a few at a time.

We've also added the ability to redo a search if you want to explore more parking spaces outside of your initial search results.

We've switched to using Google Maps which offer much clearer maps, especially when it comes to showing stations and attractions.

We've also made a number of performance enhancements.

Thanks using the JustPark app!
This release brings new designs to various screens, the ability to change times at checkout and numerous optimisations to make your JustPark experience even easier.

Thanks for using the JustPark app! This release brings a number of new features and improvements:

- You can now open the barrier at many car parks with the app - just tap on your active booking and tap 'Open barrier'.
- Space owners - you can now manage your parking space with the app. Update your availability, pricing and space details on the go in a few taps.
- Improved smart notifications when arriving at a space you've booked and to remind you when your booking is coming to an end in case you want extend.
- You can now manage your profile on the app - manage your payment methods and personal details on the go.
- Improved onboarding for new users.
- Some newly redesigned screens.

Thanks for using the JustPark app! This release brings a number of new features and improvements:

- We now show the London Congestion Charge Zone on the map to make choosing a parking space even easier.
- You can now filter your searches by space type (we’ll be adding even more filters in coming months).
- Improvements to payments and managing your booking.

Thanks for using the JustPark app! This release brings a number of new features and improvements:

* New current booking panel on the main screen that means key information and actions are always at your fingertips.
* Even faster experience for drivers paying upon arrival at our car parks: we’ve added some shortcuts and reduced the number of screens in the flow - return customers can now pay for parking in just three taps.
* Improved onboarding screens - it’s now even easier to get to grips with our app.
* Added shortcuts to find alternative parking options when your desired space is not available.
* We've also made various other usability and performance enhancements.

- We've also made various other usability and performance enhancements.

This release brings an improved user experience to our pay on arrival, pay on exit and extension checkouts. Simply use the new checkout overlay's to set your times, add a vehicle and payment method then tap 'Pay'. There are several other fixes and optimisations including a bug that prevented space owners from saving their updated pricing when editing their listing via the app, and an issue with the Apple Watch when extending an active booking.

Thanks for using the JustPark app, and if you experience any issues with this release please let us know apps@justpark.com
